ados-seleccion-colombia-masculina-de-mayores-para-amistosos/ |publisher=[[Colombian Football Federation|FCF]] |accessdate=6 November 2019 |date=6 November 2019 |language=Spanish}}</ref> The call-ups were withdrawn after the matches were postponed due to the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].\n<br>''Caps and goals updated as of 19 November 2019, after the match against [[Ecuador national football team|Ecuador]].''\n\n<!-- Organised by number (when available) position, by caps, then by most recent call up and lastly by last name. Only players called by current coach Jose P\u00e9kerman. If you remove a player please move him to the recent call ups. -->\n{{nat fs g start}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=GK|name=[[David Ospina]]|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1988|8|31}}|caps=104|goals=0|club=[[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]|clubnat=ITA}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=GK|name=[[Camilo Vargas]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1989|3|9}}|caps=6|goals=0|club=[[Club Atlas|Atlas]]|clubnat=MEX}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=GK|name=[[\u00c1lvaro David Montero|\u00c1lvaro Montero]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1995|3|29}}|caps=3|goals=0|club=[[Deportes Tolima|Tolima]]|clubnat=COL}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=GK|name=[[Iv\u00e1n Arboleda]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1996|4|21}}|caps=1|goals=0|club=[[Club Atl\u00e9tico Banfield|Banfield]]|clubnat=ARG}}\n{{nat fs break}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=DF|name=[[Santiago Arias]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1992|1|13}}|caps=53|goals=0|club=[[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]]|clubnat=ESP}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=DF|name=[[Jeison Murillo]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1992|5|27}}|caps=29|goals=1|club=[[RC Celta de Vigo|Celta Vigo]]|clubnat=ESP}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=DF|name=[[Davinson S\u00e1nchez]]|age={{Birth date and age|df=yes|1996|6|12}}|caps=29|goals=0|club=[[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]]|clubnat=ENG}}\n{{nat fs g player|no=|pos=DF|name=[[Yerry Mina]]|age={{Birth date a